  "verification_notes": "Vanessa Blair-Lewis completed her 6th season as head coach. Patriots won their FIRST Atlantic 10 Regular Season Championship in program history with 16-2 conference record. Final overall 23-10. Did NOT receive NCAA Tournament bid (notable snub given regular season title); accepted WBIT bid and lost First Round to Quinnipiac 64-71. Shares EagleBank Arena, athletic director (Marvin Lewis), and school with men's program but has separate coaching staff and roster. Coach's overall career record not verified — left null. Roster reflects 2025-26 season-end composition with one correction: 'Louis Volker' (previously in roster per Wikipedia) was REMOVED 2026-05-21 because DePaul officially announced on 2026-04-21 that Volker signed with DePaul for 2026-27 (source: https://depaulbluedemons.com/news/2026/4/21/womens-basketball-louis-volker-signs-with-depaul). 2026-27 schedule TBD.",
